OL,6,FTwo teenagers have been sentenced
OL,7,Fafter a mass brawl in a young
OL,8,Foffenders unit seriously injured a
OL,9,Fprison guard.JWith the victim's
OL,10,Fconsent, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,11,Fhas released the footage of Finley
OL,12,FPhillips and Marzin Moshen repeatedly
OL,13,Fpunching and stamping on the officer
OL,14,Fduring the attack at .JNewport Crown
OL,15,FCourt heard Phillips, then 16, and
OL,16,FMoshen, then 17, were sitting at
OL,17,Ftables in a communal area of the young
OL,18,Foffender unit on the morning of 18
OL,19,FJuly 2021, when a melee broke out
OL,20,Famong inmates.
