OL,6,FThe court heard it was triggered by an
OL,7,Finmate striking Phillips in the face.
OL,9,FRyan Young, who was a physical
OL,10,Ftraining officer as well as a prison
OL,11,Fguard, tried to break up the fight.
OL,13,FProsecutor Abigail Jackson said: "Mr
OL,14,FYoung was restraining one of the males
OL,15,Fon the floor. His last recollection of
OL,16,Fthe incident was, while he was on the
OL,17,Ffloor, sustaining a number of blows to
OL,18,Fthe head before becoming unconscious.
