OL,6,F"Finley Phillips can be seen on CCTV
OL,7,Fpunching Mr Young to the head before
OL,8,Fstamping on him.J"Marzin Moshen
OL,9,Fbecomes involved in the incident once
OL,10,FMr Young is already somewhat
OL,11,Fincapacitated on the floor.
OL,13,F"He can clearly be seen stamping on
OL,14,Fthe head of Mr Young. Both Mr Phillips
OL,15,Fand Mr Moshen were intending to injure
OL,16,Fanother male prisoner but injured Mr
OL,17,FYoung himself."JEventually, other
OL,18,Fprison officers managed to stop the
OL,19,Fbrawl.
