OL,6,FMr Young was found lying down, dipping
OL,7,Fin and out of consciousness. He was
OL,8,Ftaken to A&E where a cut on his left
OL,9,Feye was treated with glue and paper
OL,10,Fstitches.
OL,12,FHe struggled with a delayed concussion
OL,13,Fand was unable to return to work for
OL,14,Feight weeks.
OL,16,FHe was also left with scarring to his
OL,17,Feye. Since the attack, he has
OL,18,Fstruggled to sleep and has undergone
OL,19,Fcognitive behavioural therapy for the
OL,20,Ftrauma.
